---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="辐特佳新能源">
  <div class="title_section">
    家庭智能解决方案
  </div>
  <div class="cotainer">
    <div class="item_1">
      <div class="item_content">
        <div class="item_name">户用光伏电站</div>
        <div class="item_desc">
          <div class="item_desc_content">
            户用光伏电站应用于平屋顶、斜屋顶等家庭住宅场景。方案根据家庭建筑风格以及屋顶性状进行定制化设计，在赋予屋顶美观、环保、科技的同时，保障稳定供电，带来经济效益。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .title_section {
    height: 100vh;
    width: 100vw;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 100px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
    letter-spacing: 10px;
    background-image: url('/img_5.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center center;
  }
  .cotainer {
    div {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 60vh;
      .item_name {
        width: 40%;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 400;
      }
      .item_desc {
        flex: 1;
        color: white;
        position: relative;
        padding: 30px;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        .item_desc_content {
          z-index: 1;
        }
      }
    }
    .item_content {
      height: 50vh;
      width: 80vw;
      overflow: hidden;
      .item_name {
        height: 100%;
      }
      
    }
  }
  .item_desc::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: black;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }
  .item_1 {
    .item_desc {
      background-image: url('/img_3.jpg');
    }
  }

</style>

